      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MANDA KYVALLEY (8) in in fine having won her last two starts. Worked but proved too good at this venue then again raced parked before scoring at Echuca last Sunday, getting home by 4 metres. No harm in drawing here with the sprint lane to rely upon and she owns a good record here. PROHIBITED GRACE (7) put the writing on the wall when she finished third last start at Melton. Draws wide but with even luck she could pose a serious challenge. ACOOL INVESTMENT (9) is also high on the list of contenders despite a second row draw. Her best form measures up favourably in this line-up including a Kilmore win three back. Manners have been letting WITH APLOMB (11) down of late but was racing well prior so is capable enough.",
